      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "怜がお父様と絶縁状態だという話は\n{user}さんもご存じですわね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did {user}-san know that Rei and\nher father are estranged?",
        "id": ""
      },
